Using the product--------------------------------------------------------------

The website server is initiated by -
node app.js
~command on git bash.

You are asked to log in to your account right off the bat.
username: abc 
password: fgh
anything other than the above credentials would not take you anywhere.

once logged in, you are taken to the dashboard.

you may use the nav bar to navigate across the various web pages.
note that we have included a text blog in the given website.

once done, you may sign out by clicking the signout button.
